title: GREEN LANTERN CORPS Volume 1 FEARSOME (2012) (digital) (Minuteme
description:
GREEN LANTERN CORPS Trade Paperback Volume 1 FEARSOME (New 52)

Publisher: DC COMICS

(Writer) Peter J. Tomasi
(Artists) Fernando Pasarin & Various
(Cover Artists) Doug Mahnke, Christian Alamy

In this collection of GREEN LANTERN CORPS #1-7, Guy Gardner and John Stewart lead a squadron of Green Lanterns to fight a mysterious force marching across the space sectors and devouring not only their natural resources but their entire populations! Then, on a mission to rescue John Stewart and Vandor, Guy Gardner assembles the nastiest Green Lanterns to ever put on a ring!

In Shops: 7/3/2013
$14.99
